doi:10.1007/s10701-018-0165-0</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2019, &ldquo;Phase Transitions: A Challenge
for Intertheoretic Reduction?&rdquo;, <em>Philosophy of Science</em>,
86(4): 612&ndash;640. doi:10.1086/704974</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2022, <em>Emergence and Reduction in
Physics</em>, Cambridge/New York: Cambridge University Press.
doi:10.1017/9781108901017</li>

