doi:10.1093/oso/9780190946814.003.0014</li>

<li>Putnam, Hilary, 1967, &ldquo;Psychological Predicates&rdquo;, in
<em>Art, Mind, and Religion</em>, W. H. Capitan and Daniel D. Merrill
(eds), Pittsburgh, PA: University of Pittsburgh Press,
37&ndash;48.</li>

<li>Read, James, 2016, &ldquo;The Interpretation of String-Theoretic
Dualities&rdquo;, <em>Foundations of Physics</em>, 46(2):
209&ndash;235. doi:10.1007/s10701-015-9961-y</li>

<li>Rickles, Dean, 2011, &ldquo;A Philosopher Looks at String
Dualities&rdquo;, <em>Studies in History and Philosophy of Science
