42(1): 54&ndash;67. doi:10.1016/j.shpsb.2010.12.005</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2017, &ldquo;Dual Theories: &lsquo;Same but
Different&rsquo; or &lsquo;Different but Same&rsquo;?&rdquo;,
